00:31:31,420 --> 00:31:34,600
This is called the continuity equation.

863
00:31:36,300 --> 00:31:42,320
And it's the powerful principle

864
00:31:43,440 --> 00:31:45,100
that basically tells us

865
00:31:45,100 --> 00:31:47,260
