866
00:31:47,260 --> 00:31:48,220
and reappear in another

867
00:31:48,220 --> 00:31:51,820
without flowing through the boundaries of the region.

868
00:31:58,360 --> 00:32:00,580
So I could also write this

869
00:32:01,600 --> 00:32:05,020
