874
00:32:12,320 --> 00:32:14,160
You can juggle the indices up and down

875
00:32:14,160 --> 00:32:15,500
as long as you keep them balanced.

876
00:32:16,240 --> 00:32:17,560
And I won't go through that.

877
00:32:18,620 --> 00:32:20,000
But there will be times

