881
00:32:24,820 --> 00:32:25,720
with this index upstairs,

882
00:32:25,900 --> 00:32:26,780
that index downstairs.

883
00:32:26,880 --> 00:32:27,700
It's the same equation.

884
00:32:29,440 --> 00:32:29,940
Okay,

885
00:32:29,940 --> 00:32:30,440
good.

886
00:32:31,620 --> 00:32:33,060
Now let's go back

