00:51:47,400 --> 00:51:48,140
I know what I can do.

1383
00:51:48,500 --> 00:51:50,460
I can get rid of the minus sign...

1384
00:51:52,140 --> 00:51:52,580
Yeah.

1385
00:51:52,580 --> 00:51:52,660
Yeah,

1386
00:51:52,660 --> 00:51:54,700
by putting the star on the other side.

1387
00:51:55,100 --> 00:51:55,620
Yeah,

1388
00:51:55,620 --> 00:51:56,100
good.

1389
00:51:56,820 --> 00:51:57,340
Okay,

1390
00:51:57,340 --> 00:51:58,280
so that's,

1391
00:51:58,280 --> 00:51:59,080
uh...

1392
00:51:59,760 --> 00:52:00,280
That's...

1393
00:52:00,280 --> 00:52:01,540
And this object,

1394
00:52:01,540 --> 00:52:01,920
then,

1395
00:52:01,920 --> 00:52:03,920
the imaginary part of this object,

1396
00:52:04,180 --> 00:52:05,140
what is it?

1397
00:52:05,260 --> 00:52:06,720
It's the charge density.

1398
00:52:08,300 --> 00:52:08,820
Okay,

1399
00:52:08,820 --> 00:52:09,860
so let me write down,

1400
00:52:09,860 --> 00:52:10,180
then.

